├── backend/
├── frontend/
├── deployment/
└── [docs]
```

## Backend Structure
Explanation of backend folders...

## Frontend Structure
Explanation of frontend folders...

## Key Modules
- Seat Management Module: ...
- Check-In Module: ...
```

