### Additional Documentation

#### 9. Database Schema
Can be included in ARCHITECTURE.md or as separate file

**Must Include**:
- ER diagram or schema diagram
- Table descriptions
- Column descriptions
- Relationships and foreign keys
- Indexes
- Constraints
- State history tracking approach

---

#### 10. Unit Tests & Coverage Report

**Test Files**:
- Co-located with source code
- Follow naming conventions (see backend-java-standards.mdc and frontend-react-standards.mdc)

**Coverage Report**:
- Generate with JaCoCo (backend) and Jest (frontend)
- Minimum 80% coverage required
- Include in CI/CD pipeline
- Can be in `coverage/` folder or linked in README.md

